@startuml
title BP-03 - User Role and Tenant Access Assignment

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  DiamondBackgroundColor White
  DiamondBorderColor Black
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
}

|Super Admin|
start
:Select tenant;
:Select or create user account;
:Select role to assign;

|Platform|
:Validate tenant exists;
:Validate user exists;
:Validate role exists;
:Check duplicate UserTenantRole;

if (Assignment already exists?) then (Yes)
  :Return duplicate assignment error;
  stop
else (No)
  :Create UserTenantRole;
endif

if (This is default workspace?) then (Yes)
  :Unset other default access for user if needed;
  :Mark assignment as default;
else (No)
  :Keep assignment as non default;
endif

|Super Admin|
:Confirm access assignment;

|User|
:Login and receives new tenant role option;
stop

note right
Roles in current project:
- SUPER_ADMIN
- SCHOOL_ADMIN
- TREASURER
- PARENT
- STUDENT
end note
@enduml
